# =============== #
#      GODOT      #
# =============== #

## Godot 4+ (Essential)
# The .godot/ directory contains all project cache, including asset import data,
# shader cache, and resource UIDs (uid_cache.bin).
# Ignoring this single directory covers your requests for "cache", "import", and "uid".
.godot/

## Godot 3 Compatibility
# Ignores metadata files that were generated alongside assets.
*.import

## Export Files & Credentials
# Sensitive credentials that should NEVER be versioned.
export_credentials.cfg

# Packages and binaries generated when exporting the game.
*.pck
*.zip
*.apk
*.aab

## Compiled Translations
# Ignores translation files automatically generated from other sources (e.g., CSVs).
*.translation

# ================================ #
#      MONO / C# (Optional)      #
# ================================ #
# Files and cache specific to C# projects.
.mono/
data_*/
mono_crash.*.json

# ==================================================== #
#      Generic Binaries & Cache (Good Practice)      #
# ==================================================== #

## Compiled Binaries
*.exe
*.exe.config
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

## Cache and Build Folders
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]in/
[Cc]ache/
*.cache

## Operating System Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.nomedia